1. Read and create app https://ru.reactjs.org/tutorial/tutorial.html#what-are-we-building
2. Read:
   • https://ru.reactjs.org/docs/hooks-state.html  
   • https://ru.reactjs.org/docs/hooks-effect.html
3. Create todo app :
   • User can create, edit, delete, and toggle todo.
   • Use antd lib: https://ant.design/
4. Add navbar:
   Use React-router-dom lib: https://reactrouter.com/
   Pages: in progress, completed  
   Change toggle logic
5. Read about eslint, add configuration to vs code and project
6. Read about mongoDb and Nodejs
7. Create simple express server with mongoDb
   Add route todo and methods:
   GET: return todos from db
   POST: create a new todo and save db
   PUT: change completed status and update at db
   DELETE: remove a todo from db
8. Connect ui and server
9. Read about redux
10. Read about expo https://expo.dev/
11. Create expo todo app and connect with server
